Description: A spatiotemporal model that simulates the spread of Ascochyta
    blight in chickpea fields based on location-specific weather
    conditions.  This model is adapted from a model developed by Diggle et
    al. (2002) <doi:10.1094/PHYTO.2002.92.10.1110> for simulating the
    spread of anthracnose in a lupin field.
